    "body": "This is the likely culprit. \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/hyperledger/besu/blob/main/besu/src/main/java/org/hyperledger/besu/cli/util/ConfigOptionSearchAndRunHandler.java#L61\r\n\r\nYou can see that Besu only looks to `--config-file` it needs to also look at the environment variable `BESU_CONFIG_FILE` \r\n\r\nThe config file option is a special case, I suspect that the value is set correctly it's just nothing is done with it! ",
